{"tid":652531,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"奧斯卡褫奪40年前強姦犯波蘭斯基會員資格","createTime":"2018-05-04T02:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T02:08:57.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"444ad9e243bef22894725bdf76e4eda212ca6737","tid":652531,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:02:48.000Z","msg":"美國老牌黑人諧星Bill Cosby，以及著名導演、奧斯卡金像獎得主波蘭斯基因性罪行罪成，被奧斯卡組委會投票，通過褫奪他們的會員資格。負責主辦奧斯卡獎的美國電影藝術和科學學院，去年十月修訂成員的道德行為標準。學院發表聲明，指奧斯卡組委會舉行會議，根據新標準投票，通過褫奪Bill Cosby及波蘭斯基的會員資格。<br />\n<br />\n現年80歲的Bill Cosby早前被判性侵犯罪名成立；波蘭斯基就在40年前涉及強姦未成年少女，當年案發後承認犯案，其後棄保潛逃。"},{"pid":"03a2798c7057a0823d2286a055caf7936cddfe9b","tid":652531,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T02:08:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXnNOBj26lk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPXnNOBj26lk&d=r5NaYUvcD5nygBdEdwe5qi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f3467b3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PXnNOBj26lk</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}